item.title: CVE-2024-29792|2024-03-27T12:51:31.746Z -- Unlimited Elements -- Unlimited Elements For Elementor (Free Widgets, Addons, Templates)
item.description: Improper Neutralization of Input During Web Page Generation ('Cross-site Scripting') vulnerability in Unlimited Elements Unlimited Elements For Elementor (Free Widgets, Addons, Templates) allows Reflected XSS.This issue affects Unlimited Elements For Elementor (Free Widgets, Addons, Templates): from n/a through 1.5.93.
